headline: Texas Instruments Inc. (TXN) Semiconductors Tapped for NASA Radar Imaging
summary: Texas Instruments Incorporated (NASDAQ:TXN) is one of the top stock picks in Ken Griffin’s portfolio. On August 21, the company confirmed that its semiconductors are enabling radar imaging and scientific exploration payloads for the NASA-Indian Space Research Organization (ISRO) Synthetic Aperture Radar (SAR) satellite, known as NISAR.
